  <Method>
    <Step type="STEP" image="Croutons_20251126_110452.jpg">In a large bowl, toss cubed bread with melted fat until evenly coated. Add in salt, pepper, garlic powder, onion powder, and Parmesan, and toss to combine until evenly distributed. Divide seasoned bread between two large baking sheets.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Bake until golden and crispy, flipping halfway through, about 15 minutes total.</Step>
    <Step type="STEP" image="">Use, or store in a lidded container.</Step>
  </Method>
  <Variations>
